                <lg>
                    <l>The Tiny Bird flies in the Blue Sky</l>
                    <l>The Ocean mirrors the Blue of the Sky</l>
                    <l>The Deep Azure is Heaven's Ocean</l>
                    <l>In the Blue of the Sky, Heaven's Tears lie</l>
                    <l>In the Tears of Heaven, the little Bird flies</l>

